Class ZipNuclei

java.lang.Object
  org.rhwlab.snight.ZipNuclei
public class ZipNuclei
extends java.lang.Object

Instantiated in AncesTree.
Opens the zip file holding data and analyses files.
Reads data line be line from a selected file in the zip.
Holds iZipFile, an instance of java.util.zip.ZipFile and makes it available via an access function.
